TITLE: Performing BFS traversal from a specific node in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the bfsFromNode function to perform a Breadth-First Search traversal starting from a specific node. It shows basic usage and how to stop the traversal at a specific depth.
SOURCE: https://github.com/graphology/graphology/blob/master/src/traversal/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
