TITLE: Cropping Graph to Largest Connected Component in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the use of cropToLargestConnectedComponent to mutate a graph, keeping only the largest connected component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/graphology/graphology/blob/master/src/components/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import {cropToLargestConnectedComponent} from 'graphology-components';

cropToLargestConnectedComponent(graph);
```

